name: 2 2 Ind Coy Officers

desc.html:
2 2 Ind Coy Officers. Officers of 2/2nd Independent Company (Prior to Embarkation, 1941).
Back row: Lieut. D. St.A Dexter, Lieut. A. Campbell, Lieut. C.D. Doig, Lieut. J.A. Rose, Lieut. D.K. Turton.
Middle row: Lieut. J.C. Burridge, Lieut. C.F.G. McKenzie, Lieut. R. Cole, Lieut. T.G. Nisbet, Lieut. C.W. Turner, Lieut. K.G. Mackintosh.
Front row: Capt. G. Boyland, Capt. R.R. Baldwin, Capt. B.J. Callinan, Major A. Spence, Capt. C.R. Dunkley, Capt. G.G. Laidlaw.
